RELOCATION BENEFIT  
1. Please note that you may be eligible for the relocation benefit upto INR 40,000/- as a one-  
time entitlement and can be claimed either when you join as intern (if applicable) or upon  
commencement of full-time employment.  
2. This benefit is applicable only if relocation is required either from your hometown or  
college location to the city of your offered internship or Full-Time role.  
3. If accommodation and transport are provided by the company, the relocation benefit  
stands void.  
4. In case your eligibility is applicable, the breakup of the relocation benefit is as follows,  
subjected to conditions below:  
Hotel accommodation: Cost of hotel stay at Wissen/client location for 5 nights,  
effectively 6 days with a maximum cap of Rs. 5000/- per day  
Flight/train travel: Up to INR 10,000  
Other relocation-related expenses: Balance amount within the INR 40,000 cap  
5. The claim for relocation reimbursement will have to be submitted within 1 month from the  
date of relocation.  
6. The relocation bonus disbursed will be subject to refund in case you voluntarily leave  
Wissen within 12 months from the date of joining.  
7. Upon joining you may refer to the prevailing company policy for the process of  
reimbursement.
